政处罚。 注册会计师方面，财政部依据《中华人民共和国注册会计师法》，对恒大地产2018年至2020年相关财务报表审计报告的4名签字注册会计师汤振峰、魏泽、朱立为、蔡秀娟，给予吊销注册会计师证书的处罚；依据相关管理办法，对陈耘涛、吴德恩、潘国威、陈智杰、陈君瑜、卢玉捷、金莹等7名参与编制恒大地产合并财务报表的注册会计师，给予警告或罚款的行政处罚。 对于香港罗兵咸永道会计师事务所为中国恒大集团提供审计服务的有关责任，财政部将通过跨境审计监管合作机制，积极协调配合香港会计及财务汇报局对相关违法行为进行调查处理。 下一步，财政部将持续加大财会监督力度，严厉打击财务舞弊和审计造假行为，为维护社会公平正义、规范市场经济秩序、推动经济高质量发展提供有力支撑。https://content-static.cctvnews.cctv.com/snow-book/index.html?item_id=10549481356332386835&toc_style_id=feeds_default&track_id=B8E6B082-9A78-42EF-908D-FF4BE934EC18_747907742875&share_to=wechat"},"attached_info":"CkAIqvvO3cf9mtpsEAMaCTExMDUxMTUxNyDH6Y+3BjAAOLwFQAFyCTY2NzA1MjIyNngAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA","detail_text":"395 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-dcee81389ac119b51e93ee10f4b50510_xl.jpg?source=57bbeac9"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"2_1726275086.736503","card_id":"Q_665334963","card_label":{"type":"hot","icon":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png","night_icon":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"},"target":{"id":665334963,"title":"国家为什么不建个国家虚拟建筑库，把中国著名古建筑通过虚拟扫描成为建模，提供给制作3a游戏的人使用?","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/665334963","type":"question","created":1724654238,"answer_count":178,"follower_count":364,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[253,307,444,31402,63064],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"CkAIqvvO3cf9mtpsEAMaCTExMDEyOTgyNiCexbC2BjAAOOwCQAJyCTY2NTMzNDk2M3gAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA","detail_text":"389 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-96dad121be5fd198d548bb518949074a_qhd.jpg?source=57bbeac9"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"3_1726275086.736988","card_id":"Q_664292534","card_label":{"type":"hot","icon":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80